sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant Ingress as Platform Ingress<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant MLflow as MLflow Server<br/>5000/TCP HTTP plaintext
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant PG as PostgreSQL<br/>5432/TCP TLS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant LLM as LLM Provider API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 1: Experiment Tracking API Request
    Client->>Ingress: POST /api/2.0/mlflow/runs/create<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Ingress->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/5000)<br/>Bearer Token forwarded
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Auth OK
    MLflow->>PG: INSERT run data<br/>Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Run created
    MLflow-->>Ingress: 200 OK (JSON)
    Ingress-->>Client: Response

    Note over Client,LLM: Flow 2: AI Gateway LLM Proxy Request
    Client->>Ingress: POST /gateway/openai/v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    Ingress->>MLflow: Forward (HTTP/5000)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>for gatewayendpoints
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Auth OK
    MLflow->>PG: Fetch endpoint config + decrypt secret<br/>Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Endpoint config + API Key
    MLflow->>LLM: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>Auth: API Key
    LLM-->>MLflow: Chat completion response
    MLflow-->>Ingress: Proxied response
    Ingress-->>Client: JSON Response

    Note over Client,S3: Flow 3: Artifact Upload via S3
    Client->>MLflow: POST /upload-artifact<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>+ workspace resolution
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Auth OK + namespace info
    MLflow->>S3: PUT object<br/>Auth: AWS credentials (from namespace Secret)
    S3-->>MLflow: Upload confirmed
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK

    Note over Client,PG: Flow 4: OTLP Trace Ingestion
    Client->>MLflow: POST /v1/traces<br/>OTLP/HTTP protobuf<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (K8s SA)
    MLflow->>K8sAPI: TokenReview + SubjectAccessReview<br/>for experiments
    K8sAPI-->>MLflow: Auth OK
    MLflow->>PG: Store trace spans<br/>Username/Password
    PG-->>MLflow: Stored
    MLflow-->>Client: 200 OK
